<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - TransChat</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 820px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 24px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
            padding-bottom: 32px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: #1a73e8;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .header .last-updated {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #666;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        section {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #1a73e8;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e8eaed;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: #444;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }

        ul {
            margin: 10px 0 16px 24px;
        }

        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: #555;
        }

        a {
            color: #1a73e8;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .contact-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f0fe, #f0f4ff);
            border: 1px solid #c2d9ff;
        }

        .contact-section h2 {
            color: #1a73e8;
            border-bottom-color: #c2d9ff;
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .contact-info strong {
            color: #333;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px 16px;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 1.7rem;
            }

            section {
                padding: 24px 20px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Privacy Policy for TransChat</h1>
            <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: June 19, 2026</p>
        </div>

        <section>
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to <strong>TransChat</strong>. TransChat is a communication and translation platform designed to help users translate text and voice content across multiple languages.</p>
            <p>This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use the TransChat mobile application and related services.</p>
            <p>By using TransChat, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

            <h3>Account Information</h3>
            <p>When you sign in to TransChat using Google Sign-In or other supported authentication methods, we may collect:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Name</li>
                <li>Email address</li>
                <li>Profile picture</li>
                <li>User identifier</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Voice and Audio Data</h3>
            <p>TransChat may access your device's microphone to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Record voice input</li>
                <li>Convert speech to text</li>
                <li>Translate spoken content</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Audio recordings are processed only for providing translation and communication services.</p>

            <h3>Text Content</h3>
            <p>We collect text submitted by users for:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Translation</li>
                <li>Message delivery</li>
                <li>App functionality</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Device Information</h3>
            <p>We may collect:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Device model</li>
                <li>Operating system version</li>
                <li>App version</li>
                <li>Language settings</li>
                <li>Diagnostic information</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Usage Data</h3>
            <p>We may collect information regarding:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Features used</li>
                <li>Session duration</li>
                <li>Error reports</li>
                <li>Performance analytics</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use collected information to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide translation services</li>
                <li>Authenticate users</li>
                <li>Improve app performance</li>
                <li>Monitor service reliability</li>
                <li>Prevent abuse and fraud</li>
                <li>Respond to support requests</li>
                <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Firebase Services</h2>
            <p>TransChat may use services provided by Firebase including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Authentication</li>
                <li>Firestore Database</li>
                <li>Cloud Storage</li>
                <li>Analytics</li>
                <li>Crash Reporting</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Information processed through Firebase is subject to Google's privacy practices.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Google Sign-In</h2>
            <p>If you choose to sign in using Google, TransChat receives limited account information authorized by you.</p>
            <p>Please review Google's privacy practices at: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy</a></p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
            <p>We implement reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational measures to protect user information.</p>
            <p>However, no method of electronic storage or transmission over the Internet can be guaranteed to be completely secure.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Sharing of Information</h2>
            <p>We do not sell personal information.</p>
            <p>We may share information:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>With service providers that support app functionality</li>
                <li>When required by law</li>
                <li>To protect the rights, safety, and security of users and the platform</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>User-Generated Content</h2>
            <p>Users are responsible for content they submit through TransChat.</p>
            <p>We reserve the right to remove content that violates applicable laws, platform policies, or our Terms of Service.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>TransChat is not directed toward children under the age of 13.</p>
            <p>We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that such information has been collected, we will take steps to remove it.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We retain information only for as long as necessary to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide services</li>
                <li>Meet legal obligations</li>
                <li>Resolve disputes</li>
                <li>Enforce agreements</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Users may request deletion of their account and associated data.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Your Rights</h2>
            <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access your information</li>
                <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
                <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
                <li>Withdraw consent where applicable</li>
            </ul>
            <p>To exercise these rights, contact us using the information below.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>TransChat may integrate with third-party services including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Google Play Services</li>
                <li>Firebase</li>
            </ul>
            <p>These services maintain their own privacy policies.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.</p>
            <p>Any changes will be posted within the application or on our website with an updated revision date.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="contact-section">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact:</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p><strong>TransChat Support</strong></p>
                <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@transchat.app">support@transchat.app</a></p>
                <p>Website: <a href="https://transchat.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://transchat.app</a></p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
            &copy; 2026 TransChat. All rights reserved.
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
